dct_title_s: Map of part of Nipon Island to accompany Mr. Adams' report on the central silk districts of Japan
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. "The author's route is colored red". Silk districts and major towns along route are shown. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 40 (1870), pp. 339-43; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v. 40 1870.
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society by John Murray, Albemarle St., 1871.
London, 6 & 7 Charing Cross. : Stanford's Geogl. Estabt., [1870].
